1608.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;脱北者在日内瓦举行的联合国活动中揭露了悲惨的经历，敦促联合国对朝鲜侵犯人权行为采取更强有力的行动。叛逃者强调了逃亡之旅、当局的骚扰以及对家人安全的担忧。美国大使承诺提供支持，而中国则否认指控并为其行动辩护。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 06:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korean-defectors-share-human-rights-violations-in-country-at-united-nations-report/articleshow/108541608.cms</guid></item><item><title>香港法院对2019年冲击立法会的12人定罪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hong-kong-court-convicts-12-for-storming-city-legislature-in-2019/articleshow/108540363.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108540363.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 06:30:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hong-kong-court-convicts-12-for-storming-city-legislature-in-2019/articleshow/108540363.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦政府指责伊姆兰·汗的政党试图破坏与国际货币基金组织的协议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-government-accuses-imran-khans-party-of-trying-to-sabotage-deal-with-imf/articleshow/108540760.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108540760.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦部长指责 PTI 破坏国际货币基金组织协议，敦促调查。抗议者寻求领导人的释放。 PTI 批评国际货币基金组织的傀儡机构合作，并回顾促进民主协议。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 05:26:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-government-accuses-imran-khans-party-of-trying-to-sabotage-deal-with-imf/articleshow/108540760.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着游客回归，遭受危机打击的斯里兰卡经济强劲复苏</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/crisis-hit-sri-lankan-economy-shows-strong-recovery-as-tourists-return/articleshow/108540573.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108540573.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;斯里兰卡经济在 2023 年最后一个季度强劲复苏，增长 4.5%，从严重的金融危机中反弹。尽管2023年整体收缩2.4%，但与上半年负增长、下半年反弹形成鲜明对比。旅游业蓬勃发展，入境人数和工人汇款显着增加。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 05:20:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/crisis-hit-sri-lankan-economy-shows-strong-recovery-as-tourists-return/articleshow/108540573.cms</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 创建者警告称，如果应用程序遭到禁令，将会产生经济影响，称其为边缘化群体的重要空间</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tiktok-creators-warn-of-economic-impact-if-app-sees-ban-call-it-a-vital-space-for-the-marginalised/articleshow/108540257.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108540257.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;皮尔曼（Pearlman）等 TikTok 创建者担心由于中国所有权问题而遭到禁令。该应用程序改变了生活，提供了机会，并重塑了数字营销。尽管存在不确定性，TikTok 仍然是多元化创作者和社区的强大平台。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 04:59:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tiktok-creators-warn-of-economic-impact-if-app-sees-ban-call-it-a-vital-space-for-the-marginalised/articleshow/108540257.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国称苏丹：500万人因战争面临饥饿风险</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/sudan-5-million-at-risk-of-starvation-due-to-war-un-says/articleshow/108539908.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108539908.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国人道主义事务负责人马丁·格里菲斯 (Martin Griffiths) 表示，随着对立将军之间的冲突持续下去，未来几个月苏丹大约 500 万人可能面临“灾难性的粮食不安全”。他表示，苏丹军队与快速支援部队民兵之间的战斗对农业生产产生了重大影响，阻碍了贸易，导致价格上涨，并阻碍了人道主义救援的流动。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 04:40:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/sudan-5-million-at-risk-of-starvation-due-to-war-un-says/articleshow/108539908.cms</guid></item><item><title>抗议后欧盟委员会公布对农民的让步</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-commission-unveils-concessions-for-farmers-after-protests/articleshow/108537782.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108537782.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟提出气候让步，通过减轻行政负担、增加灵活性以及根据绿色新政计划修改 CAP 来解决法国、德国和波兰农民的抗议。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 04:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-commission-unveils-concessions-for-farmers-after-protests/articleshow/108537782.cms</guid></item><item><title>斯洛伐克数千人抗议公共广播公司改造计划</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/thousands-protest-public-broadcaster-revamp-plan-in-slovakia/articleshow/108538968.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108538968.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;斯洛伐克人在布拉迪斯拉发和科希策抗议总理菲科对 RTVS 的控制。部长将 RTVS 解散为 STAR 的计划受到批评。针对菲科司法系统改革的抗议活动蔓延，对法治构成威胁。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 03:40:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/thousands-protest-public-broadcaster-revamp-plan-in-slovakia/articleshow/108538968.cms</guid></item><item><title>浪漫情节高潮：如果前男友dy退出，检察官可以继续审理特朗普案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/romance-plot-climax-prosecutor-can-stay-on-trump-case-if-dy-ex-bf-quits/articleshow/108536257.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108536257.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 23:32:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/romance-plot-climax-prosecutor-can-stay-on-trump-case-if-dy-ex-bf-quits/articleshow/108536257.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯投票第一天发生反克里姆林宫抗议和逮捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/anti-kremlin-protests-arrests-mar-first-day-of-vote-in-russia/articleshow/108536250.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108536250.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 23:32:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/anti-kremlin-protests-arrests-mar-first-day-of-vote-in-russia/articleshow/108536250.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在纽约的封口费审判至少推迟到四月</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-hush-money-trial-in-new-york-delayed-until-at-least-april/articleshow/108536851.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108536851.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于证据周转存在争议，特朗普在纽约的审判推迟对他有利。对不当行为的指控和起诉书驳回论点使涉及封口费和迈克尔·科恩的案件变得更加复杂。州法院法官胡安·梅尔钱周五做出这一决定，此前一天，曼哈顿地区检察官阿尔文·布拉格和特朗普的辩护团队同意推迟审理，因为联邦检察官迟来地交出了涉及特朗普前律师、明星证人迈克尔·科恩的早期封口费案的证据。 。</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 23:53:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-hush-money-trial-in-new-york-delayed-until-at-least-april/articleshow/108536851.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯称袭击造成 20 名等待援助的加沙人死亡；以色列否认这一说法</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/hamas-says-strikes-killed-20-gazans-awaiting-aid-israel-denies-claim/articleshow/108536248.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108536248.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 23:32:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/hamas-says-strikes-killed-20-gazans-awaiting-aid-israel-denies-claim/articleshow/108536248.cms</guid></item><item><title>前副总统迈克·彭斯